{"tid":1653720,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發，求亞特巴入] 大埔富亨 及 天水圍分別有男性墮樓死亡","createTime":"2019-10-14T08:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T08:42:12.000Z","uid":268141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b84186fa7ecddbc81b037db8fa21046031a92fe2","tid":1653720,"uid":268141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDG5Ac2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDG5Ac2.png&h=22d4c762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果日報（4小時前）<br />\n天水圍天頌苑頌畫閣，早上9時18分，一名男子疑由高處墮下，倒卧地面，街坊聽聞巨響發現報警求助，救護員到場，將昏迷男事主送院，惟經搶救後證實不治。警方正調查死者身份及其墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EYjEFe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EYjEFe.png&h=1823c69d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0QNOyR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0QNOyR.jpg&h=967014a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【14:50】據了解，死者30多歲，有不良嗜好及患有思覺失調，家人指他近日沒有覆診，事發前正與家人通話，而死者並非居住亨泰樓。<br />\n【14:30】男子送院搶救後不治。早前有街坊懷疑男子是裝修工人，指他從高處棚架墮下，經消防員檢查後，發現棚架正常。警方初步調查後，相信男子從天台躍下，事件沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n大埔富亨邨亨泰樓發生墮樓事件。中午12時許，一名男子從高處墮下，倒卧在亨泰樓與富亨體育館之間的路面，街坊發現後報警，救援人員接報到場。男事主頭部出血，身體扭曲，由救護員送往大埔那打素醫院搶救，警方正調查事件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191014/60152232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191014%2F60152232&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=dbf5b665\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191014%2F60152232&h=7b4e43c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191014/60152232</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亞特蘭巴早前預言<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KAQuhsE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKAQuhsE.jpg&h=79ecaf25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea483e50c7fcebc5d5f3c370a4ba989ce4530490","tid":1653720,"uid":7312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:17:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"629c224925cb67fc3f8efb4ea819964a5b716145","tid":1653720,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e968022da1fc4a90121346dce6f10c9c41995b","tid":1653720,"uid":321041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8a2cca2bc872e235ac24206e3d50b560abc5ba","tid":1653720,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:30:20.000Z","msg":"其實咁樣大包圍d住宅區一定中幾個"},{"pid":"0c8938622734800c5fe3809f870f1aeb18581baa","tid":1653720,"uid":167419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e92ae08a667193260bba3f8ea65abf5ecc327eb","tid":1653720,"uid":268141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e8a2cca2bc872e235ac24206e3d50b560abc5ba","tid":1653720,"uid":258770,"like":0